#### `ªclone()`
Uses an array of keys or rules (see `ªpopulate()` above) to clone `subject`. 

    ªclone = (subject, rules) ->
      out = {}
      for rule in rules
        key = if ªS == typeof rule then rule else rule[0]
        out[key] = subject[key]
      out




